0x95423627A9CA598E.name: _SET_SCENARIO_PED_DENSITY_THIS_FRAME
0x95423627A9CA598E.comment:
Sets the scenario ped density to the given config.

Valid configs:
- BLACKWATER
- DEFAULT
- NEWBORDEAUX
- RHODES
- STRAWBERRY
- TUMBLEWEED
- VALENTINE
- VANHORN

See common/data/ai/densityscoringconfigs.meta for more information.
